   ``The Sands has developed a policy of occasionally presenting
non-performing entertainment attractions, and this booking fits
squarely into that category,'' Venetianer said.
   The retired Marine probably won't discuss his pending federal
trial on charges that he diverted money from U.S. arms sales to Iran
to the Contras in Nicaragua, Venetianer said.
