<BYLINE>By The Associated Press</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
   ``We're not going to open it before Christmas.'' _
President-elect George Bush emphasizing he won't make commitments to
any fresh Soviet proposals after reports that President Mikhail
Gorbachev would bring ``a Christmas gift'' to their New York meeting
this week.
</TEXT>
