understanding with the president that you are free to tell him what
you think, on any subject, `with the bark off' _ and the freedom in
practice to do it.'' _ Veteran Washington insider and former Defense
Secretary Donald H. Rumsfeld offering advice to potential White
House staffers in a Bush administration.
</TEXT>
