<HEAD>Motorcade To Include Dozens of Vehicles</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   One of the factors expected to contribute to
traffic problems during Soviet leader Mikhail Gorbachev's visit is
the size of his motorcade.
   According to police, the streets he travels on will have to be
